## <a id='overview'></a>Overview

The Heimdall Database Proxy manages SQL traffic giving improved performance and reliability up to 100x. Heimdall transparently optimizes the performance of query reads and writes while ensuring your database environment is always online. 

Deployment requires zero application code changes. Just point the application to Heimdall via an IP/port. 

## <a id='features'></a>Key Features

Heimdall Database Proxy for Pivotal Greenplum includes the following key features:

* Offloads Pivotal Greenplum by batch processing, and effectively provides materialized views
* Automates Write Master failover for Pivotal Greenplum
* Intelligently caches and auto-invalidates into Pivotal GemFire
* Routes diverse workloads (i.e. OLAP, OLTP) for optimal performance

